"  </h1>",
"  <div id=\"outline\">",
"   <ul>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10968127\">",
"      Brand Names: U.S.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10884644\">",
"      Warning",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10884646\">",
"      What is this drug used for?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10884645\">",
"      What do I need to tell my doctor before I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10884650\">",
"      What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10884651\">",
"      What are some side effects of this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
